00:30:04.743 --> 00:30:06.950
part of the United States?
 

00:30:06.950 --> 00:30:07.789
Okay, you've got some mountains.
 

00:30:07.789 --> 00:30:09.220
You've got some valleys.
 

00:30:09.220 --> 00:30:12.115
Well, somebody can give you a
function that gives you the

00:30:12.115 --> 00:30:14.390
