00:30:27.008 --> 00:30:27.578
tell you.
 

00:30:27.578 --> 00:30:32.569
So you want a pictorial
representation of this electric

00:30:32.569 --> 00:30:33.308
field.
 

00:30:33.308 --> 00:30:37.104
It's very easy to write down
the electric field at one point,

00:30:37.104 --> 00:30:40.519
namely you take that point,
you draw an arrow there;

00:30:40.519 --> 00:30:41.588
E.
 

00:30:41.588 --> 00:30:45.450
That E is the electric
