00:32:12.089 --> 00:32:12.980
It's up to you.
 

00:32:12.980 --> 00:32:13.838
You pick a few points.
 

00:32:13.838 --> 00:32:16.630
You go to another radius,
you draw more arrows.

00:32:16.630 --> 00:32:20.240
Someone had this clever idea of
